1. Nemojte *daviti* hranu, morate je dobro sažvakati. (Don't *choke* the food, you have to chew it well.)
2. Policajac je *davio* osumnjičenog dok ga nije priznao krivim. (The police officer *pressured* the suspect until he confessed.)
3. Jaka kiša je *davila* grad sinoć. (Heavy rain *pelted* the city last night.)
4. On *davi* svoju tugu i ne želi da se otvori drugima. (He *suppresses* his sadness and doesn't want to open up to others.)
5. Ne volim kad mi neko *davi* telefonima. (I don't like when someone *bugs* me with phone calls.)
6. Često se *davim* u poslu i nemam vremena za odmor. (I often *drown* in work and don't have time for rest.)
7. *Davali* su mi sedative da bih lakše spavao. (They *administered* sedatives to me to help me sleep better.)
8. Nije dobro *davati* previše novca deci da ne bi razvili loše navike. (It's not good to *spoil* children with too much money, so they don't develop bad habits.)
9. On *davljen* već dugo godina i ne zna kako da se izbori sa tim. (He has been *struggling* for years and doesn't know how to cope with it.)
10. Dajte mi malo daha, prestajete da me *davite* svojim problemima. (Give me some breathing space, stop *burdening* me with your problems.)